title: Jazirat Hulayla
description: Jazīrat al-Ḥulayla refers to an island in the Emirate of Ra's al-Khayma, United Arab Emirates that shows archaeological evidence of multi-period occupation.

properties.description: Coordinates following GeoNames for Jazīrat Ḩulaylah, representing the place Kennet describes as an island but which now appears to be a peninsula.
